place.name: KIPPEN
place.gazetteerText: Kippen vil. with ry. sta., Stirlingshire, and par., partly also in Perthshire, on S. side of river Forth-- par., 11,256 ac., pop. 1449; vil., 1 mile SW. of sta., which is 9 miles W. of Stirling, pop. 330; P.O., T.O. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
